## Clocking

The video clock (f_vi) is generated from the system crystal (f_xtal) by the clock synthesizer (U7). Early boards use MX8330MC; later revisions may use MX9911MC or consolidate both clock generators into a single MX8350.

There are three video clock configurations corresponding to NTSC, PAL, and MPAL:

